            "notes": "The deck focuses on quickly overwhelming opponents with aggressive creatures and using various disruptive spells to control the board. It leverages Juri, Master of the Revue's abilities to increase the pressure on opponents and generate advantage through creature sacrifices. The deck includes a mix of powerful creatures like Boggart Trawler and Emperor of Bones, as well as versatile spells like Fatal Push and Thoughtseize. It aims to apply constant pressure on the opponent, forcing them to react defensively while the deck continues to push the tempo and maintain board dominance. The deck's strategy is to establish a strong board presence early on and use that advantage to quickly finish off the opponent before they can stabilize."
